article.description: Texas A&amp,M-Corpus Christi 87, Texas A&amp,M International 60
article.headline: Texas A&amp,M-Corpus Christi 87, Texas A&amp,M International 60
article.linkText: Texas A&amp,M-Corpus Christi 87, Texas A&amp,M International 60
article.story: CORPUS CHRISTI, Texas -- Kevin Palmer scored 18 points and Justin Reynolds had a double-double to help lead Texas A&M-Corpus Christi to an 87-60 victory over Texas A&M-International on Monday night. Reynolds had 15 points and 12 rebounds. Palmer had eight rebounds and five assists for the Islanders (5-4). Demond Watt added 14 points and LaMarr Drake had 13 points for Texas A&M-Corpus Christi. Derek Barnes scored 14 points and Sean Tucker added 11 for Texas A&M-International (2-6). Each hit three 3-pointers. The Islanders led 46-29 at the half.
